18#include "ZXConfig.h"
19
20namespace ZXing {
21
22enum class DecodeStatus
23{
24 NoError = 0,
25 NotFound,
26 FormatError,
27 ChecksumError,
28#ifdef ZX_USE_NEW_ROW_READERS
29 _internal // this is for internal/temporary use until all 1D readers support the new Pattern API
30#endif
31};
32
33inline bool StatusIsOK(DecodeStatus status)
34{
35 return status == DecodeStatus::NoError;
36}
37
38inline bool StatusIsError(DecodeStatus status)
39{
40 return status != DecodeStatus::NoError;
41}
42
43inline const char* ToString(DecodeStatus status)
44{
45 constexpr const char* names[] = {"NoError", "NotFound", "FormatError", "ChecksumError"};
46 return names[static_cast<int>(status)];
47}
48
49} // ZXing
